				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You have to be cautious of how you use your augs.  There is planning involved in.
<br />

<br />
From an RP perspective reusable augs wouldn't mesh without how they portray the augs.  It's not sticking a gem in a socket like diablo ii.  They say that the augment is a special meterial that merges with the item to almost be like an alloy.
<br />

<br />

<br />
In the end, just be smart with how you plan your upgrade path.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=714330" target="_blank" class="postlink">Satrulis Cazictalon</a>
